og:title: Study Suggests You Could Lose Weight Eating Pizza
og:description: Losing weight can be difficult. Although there are many diet plans to choose from, many of them specify that it’s best to stick with lean proteins, fruits and vegetables. Unfortunately, that means you will have to control your pizza cravings…or will you?A new study is suggesting that eating pizza could actually help you lose weight.Study participants were placed on a diet that was limited to only 10,500 calories per week. Keep in mind that the average American man consumes nearly 18,000 calories each week.
